<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>sẖạyfyn ḥqk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- sẖạyfyn ḥqk .. tsẖq ạlʿtmẗ .. fy ạ̉rạḍynạ
 wnfws bttwb .. tnfk qywd .. mn ạ̉yạdyhạ
 ạlqrạr- jyt yạ yswʿ lblạdnạ .. wạ̉mrt hnạ bạlbrkẗ
 wʿdk swr ḥwạlyhạ .. (ạ̉mạn wslạm lwlạdhạ)2
 2- sẖʿbk ysẖhd .. kẖyr wmrạḥm .. ṭwl ạ̉jyạlh
 ytwḥd byk .. wynạdy bạ̹smk .. ṭwl ạ̉yạmh
 3- mjdk yʿly̱ .. fy wsṭ blạdnạ .. wymlk fyhạ
 wnwr ạ̹njylk .. ykẖsẖ bywt .. mḥrwmẗ yrwyhạ</lyrics>
<author>ʿạdl smyr, mạjd ʿạdl</author>
